<concept id="map_tvsdk_drm_workflow">
  <title>Implementing Primetime DRM in a TSVDK application</title>
  <shortdesc><ph conkeyref="phrases/drm-short">DRM</ph> is integrated into <ph
      conkeyref="phrases/primetime-sdk-name">TVSDK</ph>, which simplifies implementing 
content protection in a TVSDK application.</shortdesc>
  <conbody>
    <p>For an overview and details on using <ph conkeyref="phrases/drm-short">DRM</ph> to implement
      content protection in a <ph conkeyref="phrases/primetime-sdk-name">TVSDK</ph> application,
      see:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><xref href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/primetime/drm/tvsdk-drm-workflow/index.html"
          format="html" scope="external">Adobe Primetime TVSDK-DRM Workflow (HTML)</xref></li>
      <li><xref
          href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/primetime/drm/tvsdk-drm-workflow/drm_tvsdk_drm_workflow.pdf"
          format="pdf" scope="external">Adobe Primetime TVSDK-DRM Workflow (PDF)</xref></li>
    </ul>
  </conbody>
</concept>
